# VeriPatch code owners — approval roles for quality gates
#
# G6 Engineering lead: required approval before merge to staging
# G7 Release manager: required approval before production release
#
# Configure GitHub Environments:
#   staging-promotion  → required reviewer: @mnbreno (engineering lead)
#   production-release → required reviewer: @mnbreno (release manager)

# Engineering lead owns application code (staging promotion gate G6)
/backend/          @mnbreno
/gui/              @mnbreno
/tests/            @mnbreno
/scripts/          @mnbreno

# Release manager owns release artifacts and consensus (production gate G7)
/release/          @mnbreno
packaging/         @mnbreno
.github/workflows/release.yml  @mnbreno

# Governance policies
/governance/       @mnbreno

# Default
* @mnbreno
